Package: dashcam-crawler
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.13), wireless-tools, iproute2
Description: FitCamX dashcam Wi-Fi crawler and uploader
 Watches for a FitCamX dashcam Wi-Fi network, crawls video files
 from the camera, stores them locally, and uploads them to a
 configured destination (Google Cloud Storage or SFTP).
